summary: Adds a random level 80 Vampire/bear guy in ebony armor somewhere in the the Riften area.
descriptionHtml:
This mod is for all challenge seekers. I can\\\'t say that it is good, or that it works but basically, it gives you a dude named The Devil\'s Buttcheek, a level 80 vampire who thinks he is a bear. He has all ebony armor and may mess you up. He is located somewhere in the Riften area,be prepared to do some searching. Have fun!

Check out my other mod: Berry The Somewhat Angry Thieving Blacksmith

Coming soon: Shelby The Magical Dragon!!!!!
author: FoxyGrampa42
